### Hadith 3:151

*Narrated Zainab:*

(daughter of Um Salama) that her mother said, "While I was (lying) with
Allah's Apostle underneath a woolen sheet, I got the menstruation, and
then slipped away and put on the clothes (which I used to wear) in
menses. He asked, "What is the matter? Did you get your menses?" I
replied in the affirmative and then entered underneath that woolen
sheet. I and Allah's Apostle used to take a bath from one water pot and
he used to kiss me while he was fasting."

